OL,6,FThe charity boss, Charles Watson,
OL,7,Fsaid, "The agonising death of the
OL,8,FRiver Wye has unfolded in recent years
OL,9,Flike a car crash in slow motion.
OL,11,F"This magnificent watercourse, so
OL,12,Foften voted our country's most loved
OL,13,Friver, has in recent years been
OL,14,Fassaulted by a deluge of pollution
OL,15,Ffrom intensive agriculture, causing
OL,16,Fprolonged algal blooms."
OL,18,FThe Environment Agency told ITV they
OL,19,Fcould not comment on the active legal
OL,20,Fproceedings.
