OL,6,FThe Environment Agency oversees
OL,7,Fenvironmental protection in England.
OL,8,FIn Wales, Natural Resources Wales is
OL,9,Fresponsible for these regulations.
OL,10,FHowever, River Action argues because
OL,11,Fthe majority of the "Lower Wye" is in
OL,12,FEngland it is the responsibility of
OL,13,FThe Environment Agency.
OL,15,FThe hearing is ongoing.
